{"tid":2508022,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"422人次涉反修例運動囚禁 還押在囚人口創10年新高 單日還押人數最高達2,195人 懲教預期有進一步上升趨勢","createTime":"2021-04-28T12:05:43.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-28T17:32:45.000Z","uid":240362,"like":2,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"10b74fe43a6875f0821ca59248ab7ba15d3fdec5","tid":2508022,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T12:05:43.000Z","msg":"懲教署今（28日）以書面形式發表2020年工作回顧，稱案件審理進度受疫情影響，去年懲教院所收納人次較2019年減少16%，跌至11,967人次，惟因「反修例運動」案件陸續上庭，每日平均還押在囚人口升至1,962人，創近10年新高。而去年涉「反修例運動」而進入懲教院所共422人次，當中181次屬服刑人士，而其餘的241次屬還押候審人士。<br />\n<br />\n懲教署在2020年工作回顧中披露，去年全年收納至懲教院所（包括還押及定罪）共11,967人次，較2019年的14,224人次減少16%；院所每日平均在囚人口為6,902人，亦較2019年7,737人下跌11%。去年收容率則為62%。署方指，因去年上半年疫情嚴峻，案件審理工作受到影響，間接令收納人次減少。<br />\n<br />\n不過，懲教署每日平均還押在囚人口則創下近10年的新高，由2011年的1,436人上升至2020年的1,962人，增加37%；去年單日還押人數最高達2,195人。懲教署解釋，還押人數增加源於「反修例運動」被拘捕的個案陸續進入司法程序，並預期相關數字在今年會持續高企及有進一步上升趨勢。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210428/K2RL5DYETZFCFB746N7S3P3NZY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210428%2FK2RL5DYETZFCFB746N7S3P3NZY%2F&d=DgCTbN7XbHZJJfbPUwNNzZUrr29XULmfQ5XcAAvzh4c%3D&h=257854cf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210428%2FK2RL5DYETZFCFB746N7S3P3NZY%2F&h=423b2990\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210428/K2RL5DYETZFCFB746N7S3P3NZY/</a>"},{"pid":"a726b6b78b6ba81f88e9ccacf80ddd84c01ec0d1","tid":2508022,"uid":28195,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T12:08:15.000Z","msg":"多過左仔67暴動，當年炸死咗成20人"},{"pid":"7d337c0d66d3b537898304974841120e1dc62cb2","tid":2508022,"uid":251732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T12:09:36.000Z","msg":"#SENDTROOPSTOLIBERATEHK<br />\n#HKSOS<br />\n#LetMyPeopleGo<br />\n#HKEXITBAN<br />\n#GiveHKersArms<br />\n#StandWithHongKong<br />\n#MilkTeaAlliance<br />\n#FreeHongKong<br />\n#CCP_is_terrorist<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n[Twitter戰線] 煲大港共封港法案 狂推Hashtags求救<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/hbvoAS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/hbvoAS</a>"},{"pid":"43f65b654976fc0291988329990313f59a3110b3","tid":2508022,"uid":126919,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T12:13:26.000Z","msg":"旁聽&hellip;&hellip;寫信&hellip;&hellip;捐贈書籍&hellip;&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57482193453abf8995433caa73a7a471e63d93a9","tid":2508022,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T12:13:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83b46c1974775bd897f05203eca713f5987ec2ff","tid":2508022,"uid":230530,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T12:14:04.000Z","msg":"陳同佳呢？"},{"pid":"d5f0503b82bc27d146a9f5c19358afed8e4d74a0","tid":2508022,"uid":232157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T12:14:48.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a318c278671af84589eeacb2d8887e403b911fb","tid":2508022,"uid":51752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T14:59:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e37da65d4c6adaf4ceff01f23f94e127ca4d9597","tid":2508022,"uid":138964,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T16:01:50.000Z","msg":"未審先柙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />軍政府好波<br />\n揚威國際"},{"pid":"a7326299046f6ae58e16239ac1cb6c2ba6d5ac55","tid":2508022,"uid":38737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e37da65d4c6adaf4ceff01f23f94e127ca4d9597","tid":2508022,"uid":138964,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime